-- MOVES-Standard Life unit names Andrew Paisley to smaller cos group
-- 
-- Mon Aug 04, 2014 03:21PM EDT
-- None



Aug 4 (Reuters) - Standard Life Investments Ltd, the investment management division of Standard Life Plc <SL.L>, appointed Andrew Paisley as an investment director in its smaller companies team.

Paisley most recently worked as investment director, UK-smaller companies at Scottish Widows Investment Partnership, now owned by Aberdeen Asset Management <ADN.L>.